item.title: Michael Jackson - Thriller - Key of Dm
item.description: Play along video for the song Thriller performed by Michael Jackson. Chords used in the song: A7, Am7, B♭, B♭7, Dm, F, Fdim7, G, G7, Gm7, Gsus4.

item.title: Eydie Gormé - Sabor a Mi - Key of D
